data.description: Welcome to your future home in the coveted Danforth Farms neighborhood! This spacious home is a dream come true. The large kitchen, seamlessly open to the family room, creates the perfect hub for daily living and entertaining. Working from home? The study, complete with a wall of bookshelves, offers a productive and stylish space. Four generously sized bedrooms, each with walk-in closets, provide ample storage for everyone. The formal dining room is a great setting for hosting guests and special occasions. Step outside to your expansive backyard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. The 3-car garage ensures plenty of space for your vehicles and storage. Danforth Farms boasts a range of amenities, including a community pool, cabana, and a pickleball/ball court. Enjoy the convenience of OKC utilities and take pride in being part of the award-winning Edmond school district. Plus, you're just a stone's throw away from restaurants, shopping, and more. Your ideal home in the perfect location awaits!
